=== Driver ===
Portage uses the variable '''VIDEO_CARDS''' for enabling support for various graphics cards in packages. Setting '''VIDEO_CARDS''' to ''amdgpu radeonsi'' (see the [[#Feature support|feature matrix]]) will pull in the correct driver:
{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|<nowiki>
VIDEO_CARDS="amdgpu radeonsi"
</nowiki>}}

Check the USE flags of {{Package|x11-drivers/xf86-video-amdgpu}}:
{{USEflag|package=x11-drivers/xf86-video-amdgpu
|glamor+yes+yes+Enable Glamor OpenGL 2D acceleration
}}

USE flags of {{Package|sys-firmware/amdgpu-firmware}}:
{{USEflag|package=sys-firmware/amdgpu-firmware
|legacy+no+no+(if you have a Volcanic Islands GPU)Install firmware for older Sea Islands chipsets
|legacy+no+yes+(if you have a Sea Islands GPU and want to use amdgpu)Install firmware for older Sea Islands chipsets
}}


